## 4. 年度统计总览接口

### 4.1 接口描述
获取指定年度的完整统计数据，包括月度明细、分类汇总、趋势分析等。

### 4.2 请求信息
- **接口地址**: `/api/v1/statistics/annual-overview`
- **请求方法**: GET
- **认证方式**: Bearer Token

### 4.3 请求参数

| 参数名 | 类型 | 必填 | 说明 |
|--------|------|------|------|
| year | integer | 是 | 年份，如：2024 |

### 4.4 请求示例
```
GET /api/v1/statistics/annual-overview?year=2024
```

### 4.5 响应格式
```json
{
  "code": 200,
  "message": "success",
  "data": {
    "year": 2024,
    "summary": {
      "total_income": 186000.00,
      "total_expense": 105000.00,
      "total_balance": 81000.00,
      "avg_monthly_income": 15500.00,
      "avg_monthly_expense": 8750.00,
      "total_transaction_count": 620,
      "savings_rate": 43.55
    },
    "monthly_data": [
      {
        "month": 1,
        "income": 15000.00,
        "expense": 8500.00,
        "balance": 6500.00,
        "transaction_count": 45
      }
    ],
    "top_expense_categories": [
      {
        "category_id": 1,
        "category_name": "餐饮",
        "amount": 35000.00,
        "percentage": 33.33
      }
    ],
    "top_income_categories": [
      {
        "category_id": 10,
        "category_name": "工资",
        "amount": 150000.00,
        "percentage": 80.65
      }
    ],
    "peak_expense_month": {
      "month": 12,
      "amount": 12000.00
    },
    "peak_income_month": {
      "month": 12,
      "amount": 20000.00
    }
  }
}
```

